        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Medicaid Health Homes for Opioid-Use-Disorder Medicaid Enrollees Encouraged Act or the Medicaid Health HOME Act</b></p> <p>This bill extends the enhanced federal matching rate for expenditures regarding substance-use disorder health-home services under Medicaid. </p>]]></text>
      </summary>
      <summary>
        <versionCode>17</versionCode>
        <actionDate>2018-06-12</actionDate>
        <actionDesc>Reported to House with amendment(s)</actionDesc>
        <updateDate>2018-11-16T14:55:00Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Medicaid Health Homes for Opioid-Use-Disorder Medicaid Enrollees Encouraged Act or the Medicaid Health HOME Act</b></p> <p>This bill extends the enhanced federal matching rate for expenditures regarding substance-use disorder health-home services under Medicaid. The bill also temporarily requires coverage of medication-assisted treatment under Medicaid.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
